Taking to social media Andile shared how he's watched Babes grow up so fast. "It's amazing how much you've grown it feels like yesterday when you used to dance to my songs at church. I'm proud of you my little girl and your success," he said. Andile advised Babes to nurture her gift and that he wished greater things for her future. "May the Lord keep you, keep that gift growing and growing,love you mtanam Magutshwa," he added. Sweet! A photo posted by Andile KaMajola (@andilekamajola) on Dec 13, 2016 at 6:49am PST